data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET.  This gorgeous 5-bed, 4-bath residence has it all and is located in the coveted neighborhood of Cortessa! The impressive curb appeal offers a low-maintenance desert landscape, a 2-car garage, and a custom wrought iron & glass entry door. Inside we find 2 primary suites, 1 upstairs and 1 downstairs! Downstairs has a well-sized bedroom w/a private ensuite ideal for overnight guests or in-laws and full bath. Plantation shutters, and wood-plank tile flooring in all the right places. Host a feast in the large dining room.  The kitchen features granite countertops, SS appliances, a convenient island, and tons of storage thanks to its abundant cabinetry.  Relax and entertain in a low maintenance backyard with a covered patio, a built-in bar and BBQ, travertine and HEATED POOL The massive loft is great for a game/entertainment center. The primary bedroom on the upper level has a lavish ensuite w/a large dual sinks vanity, a relaxing jetted tub, and a sizable glass-enclosed shower. The spectacular backyard is comprised of an outdoor kitchen, a large bar, travertine floor, and a refreshing pool. Across the street from one of the community parks & close to the main Cortessa Park. You don't want to miss this rare find. Inquire today!
